<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema515_06_SU_0005_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema515_06.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema515_06_su_0005">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3">
          <div class="operations" lang="y">
            <div class="mixed_fraction ml_0">
              <span>4</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>3</span>
                <span>4</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            -
            <div class="mixed_fraction">
              <span>2</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>6</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            을 을 두 가지 방법으로 계산해 봅시다.
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="container_515">
                <h3 lang="y"><span class="method" circle-number="1">방법</span> 자연수는 자연수끼리, 분수는 분수끼리 계산하기</h3>

                <div class="operations_column">
                  <div class="operations">
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>4</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>3</span>
                        <span>4</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    -
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>2</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>1</span>
                        <span>6</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap frac1">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="4(9)/(12)-2(2)/(12)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap frac2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="(4-2)+((9)/(12)-(2)/(12))"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap frac3">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="2+(7)/(12)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap frac4">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="2(7)/(12)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="page page_2">
            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="container_515">
                <h3 lang="y"><span class="method" circle-number="2">방법</span> 대분수를 가분수로 나타내어 계산하기</h3>

                <div class="operations_column">
                  <div class="operations">
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>4</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>3</span>
                        <span>4</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    -
                    <div class="mixed_fraction">
                      <span>2</span>
                      <div class="fraction_box">
                        <span>1</span>
                        <span>6</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap frac1">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="(19)/(4)-(13)/(6)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap frac2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="(57)/(12)-(26)/(12)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap frac3">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="(31)/(12)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap frac4">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="2(7)/(12)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
